    {
      "id": "dc239181-c4ab-46e9-a468-7c263b034138",
      "name": "Sticky Note1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -928,
        256
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 432,
        "height": 1232,
        "content": "\n## Overview\nThis workflow is an automated birthday reminder and greeting system that checks for birthdays from Google Contacts daily at 10 AM and sends personalized birthday wishes through multiple channels. It integrates with Google Contacts to retrieve contact information, checks for birthdays occurring on the current day, and sends customized birthday messages via Telegram, Microsoft Teams, Google Home Speaker, and WhatsApp. The workflow uses Rapiwa for WhatsApp messaging and includes date formatting in Bengali locale for personalized messages.\n\n## Technical Implementation:\n### Data Sources\n- **Google Contacts API**: Used for retrieving contact information including names, birthdays, and phone numbers\n  - Endpoint: Contact data retrieval with fields for \"birthdays\", \"names\", and \"phoneNumbers\"\n- **System Date**: Uses current date to check for daily birthdays\n- **Contact Phone Numbers**: Extracted and cleaned for WhatsApp messaging\n\n### Birthday Detection Logic\n* Compares contact birthdays (stored as mm/dd/yyyy format) with current date\n* Extracts day and month components from both dates for comparison\n* Returns \"YES\" if today matches a contact's birthday, \"NO\" otherwise\n* Handles cases where birthday information is missing 🎂\n\n### Message Distribution\n* **Telegram**: Sends personalized birthday messages with Bengali date formatting\n* **Microsoft Teams**: Creates chat messages with birthday wishes\n* **Google Home Speaker**: Announces birthday wishes using text-to-speech in Bengali\n* **WhatsApp**: Uses Rapiwa service to send birthday messages after verifying phone numbers\n* **No Birthday Notification**: Sends a message when no birthdays are detected today 📱\n\n### Customization Options\n* **Schedule Time** – Change from 10 AM to any preferred time\n* **Message Templates** – Customize birthday messages for each platform\n* **Date Format** – Modify locale or date formatting style\n* **Notification Channels** – Add or remove messaging platforms\n* **Language Settings** – Change from Bengali to other languages\n* **Contact Fields** – Include additional contact information in messages "
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
